📚 Day 9 Summary
Docker Hub
Cloud registry to store and share Docker images.
Similar to GitHub, but for Docker images.
Commands learned
docker login

→ Login to Docker Hub.

docker tag local-image username/image:tag

→ Give a local image a Docker Hub repository name.

docker push username/image:tag

→ Upload the image to Docker Hub.

docker pull username/image:tag

→ Download the image from Docker Hub.

